### ==== SYSTEM PARAMS API ====
# Docs: http://localhost:5000/scalar/v1
# Base routes:
#   /api/v1/admin/system-params      — system parameter CRUD (Admin)
#   /api/v1/admin/feature-flags      — feature flag management (Admin)
#   /api/v1/feature-flags/{key}      — feature flag read (AllowAnonymous)
#   /api/v1/admin/announcements      — announcement CRUD (Admin)
#   /api/v1/announcements/active     — active announcements read (AllowAnonymous)
#
# Feature flag keys use "feature:" prefix — e.g. "feature:ai-chat"
# Severity enum: Info, Warning, Critical

# ── System Parameters ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

### List all system parameters (global + tenant-scoped)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/admin/system-params
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### List system parameters for a specific tenant
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/admin/system-params?tenantId={{tenantId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Get single parameter by key
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/admin/system-params/max_case_attachments_mb
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Get tenant-scoped parameter
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/admin/system-params/max_case_attachments_mb?tenantId={{tenantId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Update parameter value (must be IsEditable = true)
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/admin/system-params/max_case_attachments_mb
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "value": "50"
}

###

### Update tenant-scoped parameter
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/admin/system-params/max_case_attachments_mb?tenantId={{tenantId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "value": "100"
}

# ── Feature Flags ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

###

### List all feature flags (Admin — includes disabled flags)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/admin/feature-flags
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Toggle feature flag on/off (Admin)
# flagName: short name without "feature:" prefix (e.g. "ai-chat", "rtbf-portal")
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/admin/feature-flags/ai-chat
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "isEnabled": true
}

###

### Toggle feature flag for a specific tenant
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/admin/feature-flags/ai-chat?tenantId={{tenantId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "isEnabled": false
}

###

### Check if a feature flag is enabled (public — no auth, from L0 ConcurrentDict)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/feature-flags/ai-chat

###

### Check feature flag with full "feature:" prefix
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/feature-flags/feature:ai-chat

# ── Announcements ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

###

### List all announcements including inactive (Admin)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/admin/announcements
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Create system announcement (Admin)
# Severity enum: Info, Warning, Critical
# TargetRoles: comma-separated role names, null = all users
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/admin/announcements
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Scheduled maintenance",
  "content": "The system will be unavailable on 2026-03-15 from 02:00 to 04:00 UTC for scheduled maintenance.",
  "severity": "Warning",
  "startAt": "2026-03-14T18:00:00Z",
  "endAt": "2026-03-15T04:00:00Z",
  "targetRoles": null
}

###

### Create announcement targeted to specific roles
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/admin/announcements
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "New feature: AI Chat",
  "content": "AI-powered case query is now available. See training materials in the Help section.",
  "severity": "Info",
  "startAt": null,
  "endAt": null,
  "targetRoles": "Admin,GovOfficer"
}

###

### Update announcement (Admin)
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/admin/announcements/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000001
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Scheduled maintenance — UPDATED",
  "content": "Maintenance window extended to 06:00 UTC.",
  "severity": "Critical",
  "startAt": "2026-03-14T18:00:00Z",
  "endAt": "2026-03-15T06:00:00Z",
  "isActive": true
}

###

### Deactivate announcement (soft-delete via Admin endpoint)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/admin/announcements/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000001
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Get active announcements (public — no auth, cached 1min)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/announcements/active
